thread.title: Cap Gemini's Sogeti France wins contract Airbus Helicopters
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Cap Gemini's Sogeti France wins contract Airbus Helicopters | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: Cap Gemini's Sogeti France wins contract Airbus Helicopters
text:
Sept 8 Sogeti France and Airbus Group SE :
* Airbus Helicopters signs new, four-year contract with Sogeti France, wholly owned subsidiary of Cap Gemini
* Contract covers the deployment of new IT platforms supporting transformation projects including applications that connect employees, customers and suppliers Source text for Eikon: (Gdynia Newsroom)
